nodes.title: Nodes
nodes.description: These are key points where water is sourced, sold, stored, transferred, or consumed.

edges.title: Connections
edges.description: These represent the pathways through which water moves between nodes.

sources.title: Water Source Nodes
sources.description: Points in the network where water originates, such as ground and surface water.

systems.title: Water System Nodes
systems.description: Points in the networks involved in the sale and distribution of water.
